{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TCr5UQbV71oF7ZKna1e4XY","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## File Contents Report\n\nHere are the full contents of the five backend service files:\n\n---\n\n### 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settlement.ts`\n\nA settlement worker that polls the Solana chain for PHASE_LOCKED CoinflipMatch accounts co-signed by the server. It:\n- Monitors for accounts matching: correct account size (246 bytes), PHASE_LOCKED value (1), and server key\n- Reads the target_slot from the account data and compares it with current slot\n- Tracks newly discovered locked matches and transitions them in the database from \"created\" → \"locked\"\n- Logs match_detected events with target slot info\n- When a match reaches its target_slot, invokes the onSettleReady callback to handle settlement\n- Uses a polling loop with configurable interval that continues even if individual polls fail\n\n**Key constants:**\n- ACCOUNT_SIZE: 246 bytes\n- SERVER_OFFSET: 72\n- PHASE_OFFSET: 114\n- TARGET_SLOT_OFFSET: 148\n\n---\n\n### 2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n\nBuilds, submits, and confirms settle transactions. The core flow:\n1. Retrieves the secret from the database\n2. Fetches match account data (creator, opponent, algo_ver, creator_side)\n3. Fetches config account to get the treasury address\n4. Reads entropy from the entropy account\n5. Pre-computes the result using SHA256(secret || entropy || match_pda || algo_ver)\n6. Builds the settle instruction with all necessary accounts and data\n7. Submits and confirms the transaction\n8. Updates the database with result (phase: locked → settling → settled)\n\n**Error types:**\n- `PermanentSettleError` — should not be retried (missing accounts, invalid phase)\n- `TransientSettleError` — safe to retry (entropy not available yet)\n\n**Constants:**\n- PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA`\n- SETTLE_DISCRIMINATOR: `[175, 42, 185, 87, 144, 131, 102, 212]`\n\n---\n\n### 3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`\n\nMain server entry point using Hono framework. It:\n- Loads configuration from environment variables\n- Creates the database connection and Solana RPC connection\n- Sets up a health check endpoint (`/health`)\n- Applies rate limiting and authentication middleware to `/fairness/*` routes\n- Registers coinflip fairness routes\n- Starts the settlement worker with the `settleMatch` handler as the onSettleReady callback\n- Logs settlement results and errors as JSON\n\nThe worker runs continuously, polling for locked matches and automatically settling them when target_slot is reached.\n\n---\n\n### 4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts`\n\nTyped database client using the `postgres` library. Manages two tables: `rounds` and `operator_events`.\n\n**Round phases** (state machine):\n- created → locked → settling → settled\n- created → expired\n\n**Round fields:**\n- pda, game, creator, server_key, secret, commitment, tier, side, nonce\n- phase, target_slot, settle_tx, settle_attempts, result_hash, result_side, winner\n- created_at, updated_at\n\n**OperatorEvent types:**\n- secret_generated, tx_built, match_detected, settle_submitted, settle_confirmed, settle_failed, settle_retried, timeout_detected\n\n**Key methods:**\n- `insertRound()` — creates a new round\n- `updateRoundPhase()` — transitions phase with optional field updates, enforces valid transitions\n- `getRoundByPda()` — fetches single round\n- `getRoundsByPhase()` — fetches all rounds in a phase\n- `insertOperatorEvent()` — logs audit events\n- `close()` — closes the connection pool\n\n---\n\n### 5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts`\n\nConfiguration loader using environment variables. Parses:\n- PORT (default 3100)\n- DATABASE_URL (required)\n- RPC_URL (required)\n- SERVER_KEYPAIR (required, JSON array of secret key bytes)\n- AUTH_CLOCK_SKEW_SECONDS (default 60)\n- RATE_LIMIT_PER_WALLET (default 10)\n- RATE_LIMIT_GLOBAL (default 100)\n- WORKER_POLL_INTERVAL_MS (default 2000)\n- ENTROPY_ACCOUNT (default sysvar slot hashes)\n\nExports a `Config` interface and `loadConfig()` function."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aa2a148d307bea41f (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 42243\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 16739</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"65eaeb0b-2791-4aec-9b8c-bd2b8dc731bb","uuid":"b96235a5-10fc-46e1-9cf1-2a30a4a4e7a2","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the following files completely and report their contents:\n1. /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settlement.ts\n2. /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts\n3. /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts\n4. /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts\n5. /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts\n\nReport the full contents of each file.","agentId":"aa2a148d307bea41f","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## File Contents Report\n\nHere are the full contents of the five backend service files:\n\n---\n\n### 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settlement.ts`\n\nA settlement worker that polls the Solana chain for PHASE_LOCKED CoinflipMatch accounts co-signed by the server. It:\n- Monitors for accounts matching: correct account size (246 bytes), PHASE_LOCKED value (1), and server key\n- Reads the target_slot from the account data and compares it with current slot\n- Tracks newly discovered locked matches and transitions them in the database from \"created\" → \"locked\"\n- Logs match_detected events with target slot info\n- When a match reaches its target_slot, invokes the onSettleReady callback to handle settlement\n- Uses a polling loop with configurable interval that continues even if individual polls fail\n\n**Key constants:**\n- ACCOUNT_SIZE: 246 bytes\n- SERVER_OFFSET: 72\n- PHASE_OFFSET: 114\n- TARGET_SLOT_OFFSET: 148\n\n---\n\n### 2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n\nBuilds, submits, and confirms settle transactions. The core flow:\n1. Retrieves the secret from the database\n2. Fetches match account data (creator, opponent, algo_ver, creator_side)\n3. Fetches config account to get the treasury address\n4. Reads entropy from the entropy account\n5. Pre-computes the result using SHA256(secret || entropy || match_pda || algo_ver)\n6. Builds the settle instruction with all necessary accounts and data\n7. Submits and confirms the transaction\n8. Updates the database with result (phase: locked → settling → settled)\n\n**Error types:**\n- `PermanentSettleError` — should not be retried (missing accounts, invalid phase)\n- `TransientSettleError` — safe to retry (entropy not available yet)\n\n**Constants:**\n- PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA`\n- SETTLE_DISCRIMINATOR: `[175, 42, 185, 87, 144, 131, 102, 212]`\n\n---\n\n### 3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`\n\nMain server entry point using Hono framework. It:\n- Loads configuration from environment variables\n- Creates the database connection and Solana RPC connection\n- Sets up a health check endpoint (`/health`)\n- Applies rate limiting and authentication middleware to `/fairness/*` routes\n- Registers coinflip fairness routes\n- Starts the settlement worker with the `settleMatch` handler as the onSettleReady callback\n- Logs settlement results and errors as JSON\n\nThe worker runs continuously, polling for locked matches and automatically settling them when target_slot is reached.\n\n---\n\n### 4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts`\n\nTyped database client using the `postgres` library. Manages two tables: `rounds` and `operator_events`.\n\n**Round phases** (state machine):\n- created → locked → settling → settled\n- created → expired\n\n**Round fields:**\n- pda, game, creator, server_key, secret, commitment, tier, side, nonce\n- phase, target_slot, settle_tx, settle_attempts, result_hash, result_side, winner\n- created_at, updated_at\n\n**OperatorEvent types:**\n- secret_generated, tx_built, match_detected, settle_submitted, settle_confirmed, settle_failed, settle_retried, timeout_detected\n\n**Key methods:**\n- `insertRound()` — creates a new round\n- `updateRoundPhase()` — transitions phase with optional field updates, enforces valid transitions\n- `getRoundByPda()` — fetches single round\n- `getRoundsByPhase()` — fetches all rounds in a phase\n- `insertOperatorEvent()` — logs audit events\n- `close()` — closes the connection pool\n\n---\n\n### 5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts`\n\nConfiguration loader using environment variables. Parses:\n- PORT (default 3100)\n- DATABASE_URL (required)\n- RPC_URL (required)\n- SERVER_KEYPAIR (required, JSON array of secret key bytes)\n- AUTH_CLOCK_SKEW_SECONDS (default 60)\n- RATE_LIMIT_PER_WALLET (default 10)\n- RATE_LIMIT_GLOBAL (default 100)\n- WORKER_POLL_INTERVAL_MS (default 2000)\n- ENTROPY_ACCOUNT (default sysvar slot hashes)\n\nExports a `Config` interface and `loadConfig()` function."}],"totalDurationMs":16739,"totalTokens":42243,"totalToolUseCount":5,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":11899,"cache_read_input_tokens":29125,"output_tokens":1212,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":11899},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
